Easy as Bro, 
1, Open the folder with the three key gens in it, 
2, Open the FFF key gen and run it, 
3, Copy the info from the key gen to paper or notebook/word. 
4, Close the key gen.
5, Open MBAM
6, Click on register
7, Enter the info you put on paper or in notepad/word into each field
I.E: user Id = ***** and serial = ****-****-****-****
8, Hit register and all should be good, if not run the key gen again and get a new number.
